content:
The RuneScape Wiki also has an article on: rsw:Unfinished batta

An unfinished batta is created by baking a half made batta. The unfinished batta can be garnished with gnome spice or equa leaves, as specified in the recipe, to create the finished fruit batta, worm batta, vegetable batta or cheese+tom batta.

An '''unfinished batta''' is created by baking a [[half made batta]]. The unfinished batta can be garnished with [[gnome spice]] or [[equa leaves]], as specified in the recipe, to create the finished [[fruit batta]], [[worm batta]], [[vegetable batta]] or [[cheese+tom batta]].
